text.section:
For each property tax year following the expiration and nonrenewal of the Federal Nuclear Regulatory Commission license for the Calvert Cliffs Nuclear Power Plant, the applicable percentage for purposes of determining the grants under this section is:
100% for the first taxable year;
80% for the second taxable year;
60% for the third taxable year;
40% for the fourth taxable year;
20% for the fifth taxable year; and
0% for each subsequent taxable year.
